				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \Delta {\text{i}}_{{{\text{L}} - {\text{on}}}} = (1/{\text{L}}_{{{\text{eq}}1}} )\int\limits_{0}^{{{\text{DT}}}} {{\text{V}}_{{{\text{in}}}} } \Delta {\text{t}} = (2/{\text{L}}){\text{V}}_{{\text{S}}} ({\text{DT}} - 0) $$\end{document}10ΔiL - on=2VS/LDT.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
